longBusinessSummary: Treatt plc, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and supplies various natural extracts and ingredients to the flavor, fragrance, beverage, and consumer product industries in the United Kingdom, Germany, Ireland, the United States, China, and internationally. The company offers flavor ingredients, such as citrus, coffee, tea, health and wellness, and fruits and vegetables extracts; aroma, natural, and high impact chemicals; and herb, spice, and floral ingredients. It also provides fragrance ingredients, such as blends and ingredients. The company was founded in 1886 and is headquartered in Bury Saint Edmunds, the United Kingdom.
